parameters: Oh, how beautiful... your body is...

I serve Lady Dorothea, the master of Blood Moon
Castle.
What the hell is going on?!
Do you really think you can defeat me?en(v[263]>=100)

To come this far and defy me with a blade...!
Unforgivable.
It's useless to run away! And... who are you?!

Oh, \v[111]-san... You haven't forgotten about
that incident, have you...?
Ugh... Of course... I haven't... forgotten...

Ugh... Fine... I'll pretend I didn't see anything
here... Just go away quickly...

\v[111], you came all over my body, didn't you?
Don't you want to do that pleasurable thing again?
Ugh... Of course... I haven't... forgotten...

Ugh... I have no choice... I'll pretend I didn't
see anything here... Just go away quickly...

You haven't been to the main guild in the city of
Rein Garnet, have you? First, please talk to the
guild leader there.

And if you don't join the guild, you won't be able
to do any quests or anything else at this branch
guild.

Welcome, magical girls. This is the Traveling
Guild. How may I assist you?

If you have any questions or concerns, feel free
to ask.
About the leader of this village

The leader of this Blood Moon Castle is a loli-
type vampire named \C[2]Dorothea\C[0]. She is
precise, elegant, and exudes an air of
sophistication.

They have the deepest connection with demons, and
their years of research have been incredibly
beneficial not only to this region but also to
others. They are an exceptionally skilled leader
who is highly supported by the people.

It seems that regular communication from the
surveillance tower has been interrupted. It would
be advisable to meet with Dorothea-sama as soon as
possible.

Are you okay? You should have a repair kit just in
case~

Doing quests is quite tough, huh? We have to
contribute even a little bit to the guild.

Mmm...! Those nipples... they have such a nice
shape... I'm envious... mine are too big and it
feels a bit vulgar.

We magical girls can escape from enemies using
emergency portals even if we lose. Of course,
there are times when we fail, but ordinary people
can't do that... They are destined for a sad
fate...
Hey, are you okay? Did you get hurt?

It seems that the ruins of the Crimson Bloodline
are connected to another dungeon as well. I wonder
why it became such a complicated structure.
Ugh, I've had enough! Can't you wear it properly?!

Ugh, it's really tough when the enemies near the
Demon's Gate are so strong. It's scary and I can't
go inside, so how about all of us magical girls go
in together?
Oh my... You look so energetic, I'm envious.

I'm just not cut out for being a magical girl...
I'm already falling apart... sigh... Maybe I
should go to Rein's underground slums and earn
some money.

Do you think you can keep doing things like that?
You'll understand once you experience more pain,
don't you think?

The other day, my closest friend got captured by a
demon and I can't contact them anymore. They must
have become a life solely dedicated to giving
birth to demon offspring. I don't want anything to
do with that...
